data.description: Hillcrest floorplan by Seda. This welcoming 3 bed, 2 bath oasis is nestled in a family-friendly development of the Hideaway, complete with a sparkling community pool, playground, and sports field for endless entertainment. The large open floor combines the kitchen, eating area and great room. Tile and vinyl floor, no carpet! Kitchen has had a nice refresh with painted cabinets and new back splash. Nice new black hardware throughout and interior painting.  Enjoy the perks of solar panels, minimizing energy costs while embracing eco-friendly living. Top-notch schools make this an ideal location for families. Conveniently located near shopping and restaurants, this residence combines comfort and convenience seamlessly.
